data.eml:eml: Two new species of Cyrtodactylus (Reptilia: Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Thailand

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Bauer, Aaron M., Sumontha, Montri, Pauwels, Olivier S. G. (2003): Two new species of Cyrtodactylus (Reptilia: Squamata: Gekkonidae) from Thailand. Zootaxa 376: 1-18, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.157118
